tKind","docLink":"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.numLitKind","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Init/Prelude.lean#L1947-L1947","name":"Lean.charLitKind","docLink":"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.charLitKind","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Init/Prelude.lean#L1946-L1946","name":"Lean.strLitKind","docLink":"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.strLitKind","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Init/Prelude.lean#L1945-L1945","name":"Lean.identKind","docLink":"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.identKind","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Init/Prelude.lean#L1944-L1944","name":"Lean.groupKind","docLink":"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.groupKind","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Init/Prelude.lean#L1943-L1943","name":"Lean.nullKind","docLink":"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.nullKind","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Init/Prelude.lean#L1942-L1942","name":"Lean.choiceKind","docLink":"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.choiceKind","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Init/Prelude.lean#L1938-L1939","name":"Lean.instInhabitedTSyntax","docLink":"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.instInhabitedTSyntax","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Init/Prelude.lean#L1935-L1936","name":"Lean.instInhabitedSyntax","docLink":"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.instInhabitedSyntax","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Init/Prelude.lean#L1932-L1933","name":"Lean.TSyntax","docLink":"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.TSyntax","doc":"A `Syntax` value of one of the given syntax kinds.\nNote that while syntax quotations produce/expect `TSyntax` values of the correct kinds,\nthis is not otherwise enforced and can easily be circumvented by direct use of the constructor.\nThe namespace `TSyntax.Compat` can be opened to expose a general coercion from `Syntax` to any\n`TSyntax ks` for porting older code. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Init/Prelude.lean#L1924-L1924","name":"Lean.SyntaxNodeKinds","docLink":"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.SyntaxNodeKinds","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Init/Prelude.lean#L1898-L1922","name":"Lean.Syntax","docLink":"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Syntax","doc":"Syntax objects used by the parser, macro expander, delaborator, etc.\n"},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Init/Prelude.lean#L1891-L1891","name":"Lean.SyntaxNodeKind","docLink":"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.SyntaxNodeKind","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Init/Prelude.lean#L1883-L1887","name":"Lean.SourceInfo.getPos?","docLink":"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.SourceInfo.getPos?","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Init/Prelude.lean#L1879-L1879","name":"Lean.instInhabitedSourceInfo","docLink":"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.instInhabitedSourceInfo","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Init/Prelude.lean#L1861-L1877","name":"Lean.SourceInfo","docLink":"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.SourceInfo","doc":"Source information of tokens. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Init/Prelude.lean#L1853-L1854","name":"Lean.Name.instAppendName","docLink":"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name.instAppendName","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Init/Prelude.lean#L1848-L1851","name":"Lean.Name.append","docLink":"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name.append","doc":"Append two hierarchical names. Example:\n```lean\n`Lean.Meta ++ `Tactic.simp\n```\nreturn `Lean.Meta.Tactic.simp`\n"},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Init/Prelude.lean#L1838-L1839","name":"Lean.Name.instBEqName","docLink":"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name.instBEqName","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Init/Prelude.lean#L1832-L1836","name":"Lean.Name.beq","docLink":"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name.beq","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Init/Prelude.lean#L1828-L1829","name":"Lean.Name.mkSimple","docLink":"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name.mkSimple","doc":"Short for `.str .anonymous s`.\n"},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Init/Prelude.lean#L1822-L1823","name":"Lean.Name.mkNum","docLink":"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name.mkNum","doc":"`.num p v` is now the preferred form.\n"},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Init/Prelude.lean#L1815-L1816","name":"Lean.Name.mkStr","docLink":"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name.mkStr","doc":"`.str p s` is now the preferred form.\n"},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Init/Prelude.lean#L1806-L1807","name":"Lean.instHashableName","docLink":"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.instHashableName","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Init/Prelude.lean#L1803-L1804","name":"Lean.instInhabitedName","docLink":"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.instInhabitedName","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Init/Prelude.lean#L1798-L1801","name":"Lean.Name.hash","docLink":"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name.hash","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Init/Prelude.lean#L1779-L1801","name":"Lean.Name","docLink":"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name","doc":"Hierarchical names. We use hierarchical names to name declarations and\nfor creating unique identifiers for free variables and metavariables.\n\nYou can create hierarchical names using the following quotation notation.\n```\n`Lean.Meta.whnf\n```\nIt is short for `.str (.str (.str .anonymous \"Lean\") \"Meta\") \"whnf\"`\nYou can use double quotes to request Lean to statically check whether the name\ncorresponds to a Lean declaration in scope.\n```\n``Lean.Meta.whnf\n```\nIf the name is not in scope, Lean will report an error.\n"},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Init/Prelude.lean#L1758-L1759","name":"instHashableString","docLink":"./Init/Prelude.html#instHashableString","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Init/Prelude.lean#L1756-L1756","name":"String.hash","docLink":"./Init/Prelude.html#String.hash","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Init/Prelude.lean#L1753-L1753","name":"mixHash","docLink":"./Init/Prelude.html#mixHash","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Init/Prelude.lean#L1750-L1750","name":"USize.toUInt64","docLink":"./Init/Prelude.html#USize.toUInt64","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Init/Prelude.lean#L1747-L1747","name":"UInt64.toUSi