ring.csize","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Init/Prelude.lean#L1180-L1181","name":"Substring.bsize","docLink":"./Init/Prelude.html#Substring.bsize","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Init/Prelude.lean#L1177-L1178","name":"instInhabitedSubstring","docLink":"./Init/Prelude.html#instInhabitedSubstring","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Init/Prelude.lean#L1172-L1175","name":"Substring","docLink":"./Init/Prelude.html#Substring","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Init/Prelude.lean#L1167-L1170","name":"instDecidableEqPos","docLink":"./Init/Prelude.html#instDecidableEqPos","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Init/Prelude.lean#L1164-L1165","name":"instInhabitedPos","docLink":"./Init/Prelude.html#instInhabitedPos","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Init/Prelude.lean#L1161-L1162","name":"String.Pos","docLink":"./Init/Prelude.html#String.Pos","doc":"A byte position in a `String`. Internally, `String`s are UTF-8 encoded.\nCodepoint positions (counting the Unicode codepoints rather than bytes)\nare represented by plain `Nat`s instead.\nIndexing a `String` by a byte position is constant-time, while codepoint\npositions need to be translated internally to byte positions in linear-time. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Init/Prelude.lean#L1154-L1154","name":"instDecidableEqString","docLink":"./Init/Prelude.html#instDecidableEqString","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Init/Prelude.lean#L1149-L1152","name":"String.decEq","docLink":"./Init/Prelude.html#String.decEq","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Init/Prelude.lean#L1142-L1143","name":"String","docLink":"./Init/Prelude.html#String","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Init/Prelude.lean#L1138-L1140","name":"List.get","docLink":"./Init/Prelude.html#List.get","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Init/Prelude.lean#L1134-L1136","name":"List.concat","docLink":"./Init/Prelude.html#List.concat","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Init/Prelude.lean#L1131-L1132","name":"List.length_cons","docLink":"./Init/Prelude.html#List.length_cons","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Init/Prelude.lean#L1128-L1129","name":"List.lengthTR","docLink":"./Init/Prelude.html#List.lengthTR","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Init/Prelude.lean#L1124-L1126","name":"List.lengthTRAux","docLink":"./Init/Prelude.html#List.lengthTRAux","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Init/Prelude.lean#L1120-L1122","name":"List.length","docLink":"./Init/Prelude.html#List.length","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Init/Prelude.lean#L1115-L1118","name":"List.set","docLink":"./Init/Prelude.html#List.set","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Init/Prelude.lean#L1111-L1113","name":"List.foldl","docLink":"./Init/Prelude.html#List.foldl","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4